== Ikirwa cya Mazane ==[[File:Amahoro Island in Kivu.jpg|thumb|Amahoro Island in Kivu]]
Mazane ni Ikirwa giherereye mu [[Akarere ka Bugesera|Karere ka Bugesera]] 

mu [[Umurenge wa Kimisagara|Murenge wa Rweru]] ni ikirwa kivugwaho amateka menshi ameza namabi

kuko bavugako iki kirwa kubera imiterere yacyo mibi nubuzima bwabahaturiye butagenda neza<ref>http://popote.rw/ikirwa-cya-mazane-ubutaka-bwaranzwe-namateka-yubwigunge/</ref>

== Ubuzima ==
iki kirwa cya Mazane inzira zoze zijyayo ziragoye kuko ari ukunyura mumazi

amashuri ivuriro nibindi nabyo usanga kubigeraho bifashisha ubwato kuko nta modoka

